description: A local Pacific Beach family running a Gourmet Food Truck who believes in serving and making healthy choices. CHIP'S BEACH EATZ features LOCAL, ORGANIC, SUSTAINABLE products, such as Maciel Family Farm, Brandt True Natural Beef, and seafood from local fisherman John West. Chip McCarty, the owner is a San Diego native. Between Chip and his wife they have over 40 years experience in the restaurant industry. Chef Chip is culinary trained and has held Chef positions at Valley View Casino and Hard Rock Hotel to name a few.  If you every want to take a tour of the truck just ask Chef Chip he would love to show you around.
name: Chip's Beach Eatz
